body:
A warning like this is not expected.  It says that a pending (not yet
complete) Collective operation was aborted because somewhere else during
the step an Out-of-range error status occurred.   The exact origin of this
kind of error status can be hard to track down.  You should look at the
logs of all of the worker processes and try to find the first time at which
an error status arises.
